OL,5, The growing gap between the UK's "haves
OL,6, and have-nots" is in danger of becoming
OL,7, a "chasm", a report has warned.        
OL,9,FResearch by the Centre for Social      
OL,10,FJustice (CSJ) think tank argues the    
OL,11,Fmost disadvantaged are no better off   
OL,12,Fthan they were 15 years ago.           
OL,14,FIt highlights issues including stagnant
OL,15,Fwages, family breakdown, poor housing, 
OL,16,Fcrime and mental health problems.      
OL,18,FThe government said it had provided    
OL,19,Fsupport to help with the rising cost of
OL,20,Fliving.                                
